  "prompt": "What are the best residential schools from class 9 in Hyderabad / Secunderabad? With low fees",
  "response": "Finding the best residential schools in Hyderabad/Secunderabad for class 9 with affordable fees can be a bit challenging, as the definition of \"best\" varies based on individual needs, preferences, and priorities. However, here are a few reputed residential schools in the region that offer quality education at relatively lower fees compared to premium institutions:\n\n---\n\n### **1. Narayana e-Techno School (Residential Campus)**\n   - **Location:** Shameerpet, Hyderabad\n   - **Key Features:** Focus on academics, affordable fees, and residential facilities.\n   - **Fee Range:** Moderate (varies based on facilities and grade)\n   - Website: [www.narayanagroup.com](https://www.narayanagroup.com)\n\n---\n\n### **2. Little Flower High School (Residential Wing)**\n   - **Location:** Uppal, Hyderabad\n   - **Key Features:** Strong academic foundation, disciplined environment, and reasonable fees.\n   - **Fee Range:** Affordable\n   - Website: [www.littleflowerhighschool.com](https://www.littleflowerhighschool.com)\n\n---\n\n### **3. Vishwa Vidyapeeth Group of Schools (Residential Campus)**\n   - **Location:** Gandipet, Hyderabad\n   - **Key Features:** Holistic education, sports, and extracurricular activities.\n   - **Fee Range:** Moderate\n   - Website: [www.vishwaliya.com](https://www.vishwaliya.com)\n\n---\n\n### **4. Future Kids School (Residential Facility)**\n   - **Location:** Keesara, Hyderabad\n   - **Key Features:** Focus on academic excellence and co-curricular activities.\n   - **Fee Range:** Affordable\n   - Website: [www.futurekids.in](https://www.futurekids.in)\n\n---\n\n### **5. Jubilee Hills Public School (Balaji Residential Campus)**\n   - **Location:** Kompally, Hyderabad\n   - **Key Features:** Good infrastructure, balanced curriculum, and affordable fees.\n   - **Fee Range:** Moderate\n   - Website: [www.jhps.com](https://www.jhps.com)\n\n---\n\n### **6. Chirec International School (Residential Facility)**\n   - **Location:** Kondapur, Hyderabad\n   - **Key Features:** ICSE and CBSE boards, excellent faculty, and reasonable fees for a residential school.\n   - **Fee Range:** Moderate (higher than others but still accessible)\n   - Website: [www.chirec.ac.in](https://www.chirec.ac.in)\n\n---\n\n### **7. Global Edge School (Residential Campus)**\n   - **Location:** Shamirpet, Hyderabad\n   - **Key Features:** Focus on academics, sports, and personality development.\n   - **Fee Range:** Affordable\n   - Website: [www.globaledgeschool.com](https://www.globaledgeschool.com)\n\n---\n\n### **Tips for Selecting a School:**\n1. **Visit the Campus:** Check the infrastructure, cleanliness, and safety measures.\n2. **Compare Fees:** Ask for a detailed fee structure, including hostel charges, academics, and extracurriculars.\n3. **Academics and Extracurriculars:** Ensure the school offers a balanced curriculum.\n4. **Talk to Alumni/Current Students:** Get insights into the school\u2019s environment and culture.\n5. **Check Reviews:** Look for online reviews and parent feedback.\n\n---\n\nIt\u2019s advisable to contact the schools directly for the latest fee structure and admission details, as fees may vary based on facilities and grade level.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
